4 text-lg"><a class="rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-light text-stone-600 hover:text-stone-900" href="/publications">Publications</a><a class="rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-light text-stone-600 hover:text-stone-900" href="/team">Team</a><a class="rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-light text-stone-600 hover:text-stone-900" href="/news">News</a><a class="rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-light text-stone-600 hover:text-stone-900" href="/courses">Courses</a></div></nav></div><div class="pt-16"><section id="adriana-bio" class="py-12 bg-stone-50"><div class="layout"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[fit-content(256px)_1fr] gap-12"><div class=""><div class=""><div class="w-full max-w-[256px] h-auto mx-auto md:mx-0 mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-300 shadow-lg"><img alt="Profile picture of Adriana" loading="lazy" width="256" height="256" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="h-full w-full object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fprofile%2Fadriana-full.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fprofile%2Fadriana-full.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fprofile%2Fadriana-full.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75"/></div><div class="text-sm text-stone-700 space-y-1 text-center md:text-left"><div>Associate Professor</div><div>Brown University</div><div>adriana_schulz [at] brown.edu</div></div></div></div><div class=""><h2 class="mb-6 text-5xl font-bold text-stone-800 tracking-tight">Adriana Schulz</h2><div class="prose prose-stone prose-a:no-underline max-w-none"><p>I am an Associate Professor of <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://cs.brown.edu/" class="animated-underline custom-link text-primary-700 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:rounded focus-visible:ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 border-dark border-b border-dotted hover:border-black/0">Computer Science</a> at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://brown.edu/" class="animated-underline custom-link text-primary-700 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:rounded focus-visible:ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 border-dark border-b border-dotted hover:border-black/0">Brown University</a> and a member of the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://visual.cs.brown.edu/" class="animated-underline custom-link text-primary-700 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:rounded focus-visible:ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 border-dark border-b border-dotted hover:border-black/0">Brown Visual Computing</a> group. I am also an affiliate faculty at the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.cs.washington.edu/" class="animated-underline custom-link text-primary-700 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:rounded focus-visible:ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 border-dark border-b border-dotted hover:border-black/0">Paul G. Allen School of Computer Science &amp; Engineering</a> at the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.washington.edu/" class="animated-underline custom-link text-primary-700 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:rounded focus-visible:ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 border-dark border-b border-dotted hover:border-black/0">University of Washington</a> and the chair of <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.wigraph.org/" class="animated-underline custom-link text-primary-700 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:rounded focus-visible:ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 border-dark border-b border-dotted hover:border-black/0">WiGRAPH</a>.</p>
<p>My research group creates design tools and systems that will revolutionize how we build physical artifacts. A central challenge for design tools in manufacturing is the need to simultaneously nurture the creative ability to conceive novel designs and the analytical capacity to critically evaluate and optimize functionality and production. My group tackles this challenge through innovative solutions that are grounded in the fundamentals of geometry processing and combine insights from machine learning and programming languages.</p>
<p>My research has been recognized by the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://sloan.org/fellowships/2024-Fellows" class="animated-underline custom-link text-primary-700 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:rounded focus-visible:ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 border-dark border-b border-dotted hover:border-black/0">Alfred P. Sloan Foundation Fellowship</a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.technologyreview.com/innovator/adriana-schulz/" class="animated-underline custom-link text-primary-700 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:rounded focus-visible:ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 border-dark border-b border-dotted hover:border-black/0">MIT Technology Review&#x27;s Innovators Under 35 award</a>, an NSF CAREER award, and faculty awards from Google, Amazon, and Intel, among others. I am honored to receive the <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.siggraph.org/awards/significant-new-researcher-award/2024" class="animated-underline custom-link text-primary-700 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:rounded focus-visible:ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 border-dark border-b border-dotted hover:border-black/0">2024 ACM SIGGRAPH Significant New Researcher Award</a>.</p><div class="flex flex-col mt-4 gap-4 items-start"><a class="rounded font-medium focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring shadow-sm transition-colors duration-75 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm md:text-base bg-white text-stone-700 border border-stone-300 hover:text-dark hover:bg-stone-100 active:bg-white/80 disabled:bg-stone-200 disabled:cursor-not-allowed group gap-[0.25em] inline-flex items-center" href="/"><span>View my Publications, News, and more</span><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" height="1em" width="1em" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="relative transition-transform duration-200 motion-safe:-translate-x-1 group-hove